turecdn.net/KJAUJNT2XrwbghYaQ3EJ76-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/KJAUJNT2XrwbghYaQ3EJ76.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/KJAUJNT2XrwbghYaQ3EJ76.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: Meaco)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eWhile I still love the misting function on the Flexbreeze HydroGo, for what I use a portable fan for, the Meaco seemed to outdo it and here\u0026#39;s why.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv data-hydrate=\"true\" id=\"slice-container-newsletterForm-articleInbodyContent-4ReSJEJtnWjZioXmYbu54K\"\u003e\u003csection\u003e\u003cp\u003eSign up to our newsletter for style and decor inspiration, house makeovers, project advice and more.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/section\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003eMeaco \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/tag/fans\" data-auto-tag-linker=\"true\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/tag/fans\"\u003efans\u003c/a\u003e have always been known for their quiet operation, and this model is no exception to this \u0026#39;whisper-quiet\u0026#39; rep, delivering ultra-quiet airflow from just 26.9dB.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eEven on high speeds, the sound is a soft whoosh, if anything and works well when on calls at your desk or having it on to cool down a babe as they sleep.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RHpPThGswsYavQryqdPCxL-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RHpPThGswsYavQryqdPCxL-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RHpPThGswsYavQryqdPCxL-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RHpPThGswsYavQryqdPCxL-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RHpPThGswsYavQryqdPCxL-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RHpPThGswsYavQryqdPCxL-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RHpPThGswsYavQryqdPCxL-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RHpPThGswsYavQryqdPCxL-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RHpPThGswsYavQryqdPCxL.jpg\" alt=\"meaco sefte 8 portable fan side angle\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RHpPThGswsYavQryqdPCxL-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RHpPThGswsYavQryqdPCxL-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RHpPThGswsYavQryqdPCxL-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RHpPThGswsYavQryqdPCxL-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RHpPThGswsYavQryqdPCxL-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RHpPThGswsYavQryqdPCxL-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RHpPThGswsYavQryqdPCxL-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RHpPThGswsYavQryqdPCxL-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RHpPThGswsYavQryqdPCxL.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/RHpPThGswsYavQryqdPCxL.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: Meaco)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eI also love the night mode, which dims the display right down and reduces the fan speed incrementally as you sleep. Plus, the eco-mode is also a standout feature to shout about. It automatically adjusts the fan speed to the room temperature, so you get just the right amount of chill.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eAnd with that functionality, it saves energy and means I\u0026#39;m not fiddling with the settings. Speaking of eco, it also uses as little as 1 watt, and runs for less than 1p per hour. How\u0026#39;s that for keeping \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/news/how-much-does-it-cost-to-run-a-fan-2-253322\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/news/how-much-does-it-cost-to-run-a-fan-2-253322\"\u003efan running costs\u003c/a\u003e down?\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mHYn5rrp3Eb49tU8wLTX3c-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mHYn5rrp3Eb49tU8wLTX3c-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mHYn5rrp3Eb49tU8wLTX3c-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mHYn5rrp3Eb49tU8wLTX3c-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mHYn5rrp3Eb49tU8wLTX3c-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mHYn5rrp3Eb49tU8wLTX3c-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mHYn5rrp3Eb49tU8wLTX3c-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mHYn5rrp3Eb49tU8wLTX3c-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mHYn5rrp3Eb49tU8wLTX3c.jpg\" alt=\"meaco sefte 8 portable fan on a coffee table in a living room\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mHYn5rrp3Eb49tU8wLTX3c-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mHYn5rrp3Eb49tU8wLTX3c-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mHYn5rrp3Eb49tU8wLTX3c-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mHYn5rrp3Eb49tU8wLTX3c-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mHYn5rrp3Eb49tU8wLTX3c-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mHYn5rrp3Eb49tU8wLTX3c-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mHYn5rrp3Eb49tU8wLTX3c-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mHYn5rrp3Eb49tU8wLTX3c-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mHYn5rrp3Eb49tU8wLTX3c.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/mHYn5rrp3Eb49tU8wLTX3c.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: Meaco)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eOK, it may not be weatherproof like the Shark fan, so it may not be suitable for outdoors during intermittent showers, and may not have the extra cooling mist included, but the Sefte 8\u0026#34; delivers a genuinely quiet, effective breeze all day long and doesn\u0026#39;t take up much space while doing it. That counts for a lot in my book.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigure data-bordeaux-image-check=\"\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource type=\"image/webp\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TXBLFcMcpBY8LWn4N6CJD9-1920-80.jpg.webp 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TXBLFcMcpBY8LWn4N6CJD9-1600-80.jpg.webp 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TXBLFcMcpBY8LWn4N6CJD9-1280-80.jpg.webp 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TXBLFcMcpBY8LWn4N6CJD9-1024-80.jpg.webp 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TXBLFcMcpBY8LWn4N6CJD9-768-80.jpg.webp 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TXBLFcMcpBY8LWn4N6CJD9-415-80.jpg.webp 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TXBLFcMcpBY8LWn4N6CJD9-360-80.jpg.webp 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TXBLFcMcpBY8LWn4N6CJD9-320-80.jpg.webp 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\"/\u003e\u003cimg src=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TXBLFcMcpBY8LWn4N6CJD9.jpg\" alt=\"Meaco sefte portable fan on a coffee table with books and glasses\" srcset=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TXBLFcMcpBY8LWn4N6CJD9-1920-80.jpg 1920w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TXBLFcMcpBY8LWn4N6CJD9-1600-80.jpg 1600w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TXBLFcMcpBY8LWn4N6CJD9-1280-80.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TXBLFcMcpBY8LWn4N6CJD9-1024-80.jpg 1024w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TXBLFcMcpBY8LWn4N6CJD9-768-80.jpg 768w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TXBLFcMcpBY8LWn4N6CJD9-415-80.jpg 415w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TXBLFcMcpBY8LWn4N6CJD9-360-80.jpg 360w, https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TXBLFcMcpBY8LWn4N6CJD9-320-80.jpg 320w\" sizes=\"(min-width: 710px) 670px, calc(100vw - 30px)\" loading=\"lazy\" data-original-mos=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TXBLFcMcpBY8LWn4N6CJD9.jpg\" data-pin-media=\"https://cdn.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/TXBLFcMcpBY8LWn4N6CJD9.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp\u003e(Image credit: Meaco)\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\u003cp\u003eNeedless to say, it\u0026#39;s a go-to heatwave appliance, giving even the Shark a run for its money. And with it retailing at £79.99, it\u0026#39;s £50 cheaper than the FlexBreeze HydroGo too, even when \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/renovation/heating-and-cooling/shark-flexbreeze-hydrogo-misting-fan-deal-june-2025\" data-before-rewrite-localise=\"https://www.idealhome.co.uk/renovation/heating-and-cooling/shark-flexbreeze-hydrogo-misting-fan-deal-june-2025\"\u003eit\u0026#39;s on sale\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp\u003eYou can pick one up with a nifty little storage bag on \u003ca data-analytics-id=\"inline-link\" href=\"https://www.awin1.com/awclick.php?awinmid=31711\u0026amp;awinaffid=103504\u0026amp;clickref=idealhome-gb-3425560224196200414\u0026amp;p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.meaco.com%2Fproducts%2Fsefte-8-portable-battery-air-circulator\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"sponsored noopener\" data-url=\"https://www.meaco.com/products/sefte-8-portable-battery-air-circulator\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\" data-hl-processed=\"hawklinks\" data-placeholder-url=\"https://www.awin1.com/awclick.php?awinmid=31711\u0026amp;awinaffid=103504\u0026amp;clickref=hawk-custom-tracking\u0026amp;p=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.meaco.com%2Fproducts%2Fsefte-8-portable-battery-air-circulator\" data-google-interstitial=\"false\" data-merchant-name=\"Meaco UK\" data-merchant-id=\"281134\" da